reviewText: Just love watching them perform. Great viewing and sound
The dvd played for a few minutes and then stopped working. Waste of money and it was a Christmas present.
We love this DVD. We always love to watch your DVD's.

I love the McKamey's but somewhere over the course of time as I have collected their live concerts on video, I somehow missed this one. Very good addition to my collection. Professional sound and video quality and the onstage performance is classic McKamey's. If you like the McKamey's you'll love this project from one of Southern Gospel Music's leading family groups. Highly Recommend.
We bought 2 dvds at a great price and would buy more if We could find them We love the McKameys singing
Excellent Quality and a Superb Live Performance from one of Gospel Music's finest groups! A highly cherished part of my Gospel collection!
